l.jpg\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"type\">Cyflwynwyd gan</span><span class=\"name\">Richard Harrington</span></p></div></a></div><div class=\"\n                k-promo promo-6 gel\"><a href=\"http://www.developingdylan100.co.uk/cy/\"><div class=\"media\"><img class=\"resp widescreen\" src=\"http://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/256x144/p01y8c4l.jpg\" data-pid=\"p01y8c4l\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"k-g-sprite icon k-link\">Visit</span><span class=\"overlay\"></span></div><div class=\"context\"><span class=\"genre k-type-body-index\">Celfyddydau a Diwylliant</span><p class=\"title\n                            k-type-sub-header\">Dylanwad100</p></div></a></div></div></div></div></section><footer class=\"k-g-footer\"><div id=\"k-g-gn-footer\"><ol class=\"k-g-gn\"><li><a href=\"#zc844wx\">Traddodiad barddol Dylan Thomas</a></li><li><a href=\"#z8mqq6f\">Cynghanedd cerddi Dylan</a></li><li><a href=\"#z9wkkqt\">Oedd Dylan yn siarad Cymraeg?</a></li><li><a href=\"#z8hxxnb\">Sŵn a swyn y geiriau</a></li><li><a href=\"#zqshhyc\">Nid ar chwarae bach</a></li><li><a href=\"#z8qdd2p\">Gwrandewch</a></li><li><a href=\"#zs9rr82\">Beth ydych chi'n ei feddwl?</a></li><li><a href=\"#zghxxnb\">Ble nesaf?</a></li></ol></div><div class=\"k-g-lp\"><div class=\"k-g-lp-options\"><span>Languages:</span><a href=\"/guides/language/cy/zybyyrd\">Cymraeg</a><a href=\"/guides/language/gd/zybyyrd\">Gàidhlig</a><a href=\"/guides/language/ga/zybyyrd\">Gaeilge</a></div></div></footer></div>\n\n  </div>       </div> <div id=\"orb-footer\"  class=\"orb-footer orb-footer-grey\" > <aside role=\"complementary\"> <div id=\"orb-aside\" class=\"orb-nav-sec b-r b-g-p\"> <div class=\"orb-footer-inner\" role=\"navigation\"> <h2 class=\"orb-footer-lead\">Explore the BBC</h2>  <div id=\"orb-footer-promo\" class=\"orb-d\"></div>  <div class=\"orb-footer-primary-links\"> <ul>    <li  class=\"orb-nav-news orb-d\"  > <a href=\"/news/\">News</a> </li>    <li  class=\"orb-nav-newsdotcom orb-w\"  > <a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/news/